ABRT Docker container
=====================

Features
--------
* Detection of core dump files
* Detection of kernel oopses in journalctl
* Detection of kernel vmcores on host's file system
* E-mail notifications

Installation
------------
# docker run --rm --privileged -v /:/host IMAGE /usr/local/bin/abrt-install.sh

Un-installation
---------------
# docker run --rm --privileged -v /:/host IMAGE /usr/local/bin/abrt-uninstall.sh

Run
---
# docker run -d --privileged -v /dev/log:/dev/log -v /var/run/systemd/journal/socket:/var/run/systemd/journal/socket -v /:/host -v /var/run/abrt:/var/run/abrt --pid=host --net=host --name NAME IMAGE

Configuration
-------------
Pass `-e ABRT_VERBOSE=NUM` on the run command line to make abrt producing more logs.
